OL,3,CGeneral Election 2024: A look at the
OL,4,Cancient city battling modern problems
OL,6,FCaron Bell reports on the modern
OL,7,Fissues facing the ancient city of
OL,8,FGloucester
OL,10,FIn every general election since 1979,
OL,11,FGloucester has voted in an MP from the
OL,12,Fsame party as the Government.
OL,14,FThe polls suggest a strong swing to
OL,15,FLabour this year, but whoever wins
OL,16,Fthis bellwether seat will take on a
OL,17,Fcomplicated constituency that mixes
OL,18,Fancient heritage with modern-day
OL,19,Fproblems.
