OL,3,CGeneral Election 2024: A look at the
OL,4,Cancient city battling modern problems
OL,6,FChief among them in the historic city
OL,7,Fis the battle to keep the city centre
OL,8,Fthriving.
OL,10,FWestgate Street, in the heart of the
OL,11,Fold city, has seven empty shops in a
OL,12,Frow.
OL,14,FAdrian Ball's family has run a hair
OL,15,Fsalon on nearby Southgate Street since
OL,16,F1967.
OL,18,F"Something needs to be done because
OL,19,Fthe city centre, we worry, might
OL,20,Fbecome a ghost town", he told ITV News.
