OL,6,F"A new government could come up with
OL,7,Fsome incentives to encourage people to
OL,8,Fget into a city centre and reopen new
OL,9,Fshops", he added.
OL,11,FThe skyline is dominated by
OL,12,FGloucester's 11th-century cathedral.
OL,13,FNestled in an alleyway is the Tailor
OL,14,Fof Gloucester's shop, the setting for
OL,15,Fone of Beatrix Potter's best-loved
OL,16,Fstories.
OL,18,FTourists come from around the world to
OL,19,Fvisit both.
