OL,6,F"Unfortunately there is a really,
OL,7,Freally dark undercurrent in this city,
OL,8,Fand that is knife crime and gangs,"
OL,9,Fexplains Delroy Ellis, founder of Yes
OL,10,FMentoring, which works with local
OL,11,Fteenagers. "And a large percentage of
OL,12,Fyoung people - mainly males - are
OL,13,Fdisenfranchised and don't have
OL,14,Fpositive role models."
